ery function a canonical envelope that is in some sense as\nclose as possible to a uniform envelope. We obtain a composition theorem\nsimilar to the uniform case.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Mar 2021 08:30:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 May 2022 15:16:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 6 Jun 2022 17:08:34 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 20 Jun 2022 13:42:39 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 27 Jul 2022 16:16:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-28"}
