r method is currently being applied to\ndifferent Stage~III lensing surveys, and can easily be extended to Stage~IV\nlensing surveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Mar 2021 09:53:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Apr 2021 08:02:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 20 Sep 2021 07:52:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-21"}
