g the complex behavior of\nmultiple SMBHs in galactic mergers, as such systems cannot be readily modeled\nusing simple orbit-averaged semi-analytic models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Mar 2021 11:09:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 May 2021 11:10:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-07"}
