 results further confirm the time tested belief that security through\nobscurity is not a long term solution and leaves such platforms open to piracy\nand a subsequent loss of revenue for all the stakeholders.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Mar 2021 14:01:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-31"}
